{"tid":1966000,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多連登仔覺得所有香港後生都上連登？","createTime":"2020-04-10T00:12:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T10:00:07.000Z","uid":20442,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d94697f2c3a291cf17718ef3ba04e62c50153527","tid":1966000,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T00:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全香港6 成黃絲，800 萬人*60%，480 萬人日日上連登。<br />\n<br />\n好多posts：「連登仔食元氣」、「連登仔搵行貨switch ，全部垃圾」、「連登仔xxxx」⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n香港任何後生都可以化身連登仔嗎？做人切忌井底之蛙，香港好多人冇上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">簡單啲建議，字多又冇人睇。<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔好當連登全香港上，有乜香港民情都上嚟「屌全連登」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 出posts嘅人改做呼籲、建議、行動posts、xx戰線，而唔好「連登仔冇骨氣前」，「連登仔垃圾後」<br />\n<br />\n3. 跳出圍爐取暖心態，請上Twitter 、入TVB戰線、成為貼紙師，擴張版圖好過圍爐取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"26e36a4aafb3037a9c7915de9c46ef1d2a1ccb31","tid":1966000,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T00:35:12.000Z","msg":"得學生上<br />\n<br />\n在職果d好多都忙"},{"pid":"8853d4442704db5a41c4f4062cf5c6cc374415b4","tid":1966000,"uid":63311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T00:36:08.000Z","msg":"廢青多"},{"pid":"ba8bd8a93a34e9755d793ab079f1549acc53be32","tid":1966000,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T00:44:15.000Z","msg":"無可能冇上"},{"pid":"bdaeef02a4b574e2d6014890e25dd782b43d3c76","tid":1966000,"uid":215043,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26e36a4aafb3037a9c7915de9c46ef1d2a1ccb31","tid":1966000,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T00:35:12.000Z","msg":"得學生上<br />\n<br />\n在職果d好多都忙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T00:56:16.000Z","msg":"無咁嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{